description: This file defines a team of agents and evaluates their reliability in fetching stock information using OpenAI models and YFinance tools.

classes.name: Agent
classes.description: Represents an agent with a name, model, role, and tools.

classes.name: Team
classes.description: Represents a team of agents with a name, model, members, and display options.

classes.name: TeamRunResponse
classes.description: Encapsulates the response from running a team.

classes.name: ReliabilityEval
classes.description: Evaluates the reliability of a team response based on expected tool calls.

classes.name: ReliabilityResult
classes.description: Contains the result of a reliability evaluation, with methods to assert pass/fail.

classes.name: YFinanceTools
classes.description: Tools for fetching stock data from Yahoo Finance.

methods.name: evaluate_team_reliability
methods.description: Runs the reliability evaluation for the stock research team.
